    "image_with_text_wKVLmh": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_CLbqn8": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2>Q&A with May Ann</h2><h3>Q: What are 3 words your friends or family would use to describe you?</h3><p>A: Crazy, loud, and funny.</p><h3>Q: Tell us the story behind Studio Fundamentals.</h3><p>A: Studio Fundamentals started in 2017 with the intent of documenting my design work. It began as graphic design, then evolved from 2D design to what it is now—pottery.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
